description: Aspose.TeX Convert Micro Application allows you to convert your TeX and LaTeX documents via the command line or add a TeX convert feature to your .NET application.
summary: Aspose.TeX Convert Micro Application allows converting TeX and LaTeX documents to various formats such as PDF, XPS, PNG, JPEG, BMP, TIFF, and SVG. It enhances your .NET applications, enabling document conversions directly or via command line without detailed coding. Works on any .NET compatible OS.
